aiHeadline: Data Retrieval Challenges in Causal News Analysis
aiBlurb: Attempts to gather economy and agriculture news from early March 2025 faced technical difficulties, preventing the generation of causal predictions. Alternative methods or tools may be needed for successful data collection.

predictions.article: China hits U.S. agriculture with tariffs March 2025
predictions.prediction: U.S. soybean and sorghum exports to China will decrease by over 90% within the next month due to the high tariffs imposed by China.
